{"tid":58533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷八達通退款$150　老差骨判囚勢失長俸","createTime":"2016-12-29T01:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T03:11:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55694e5a78fb37615fe908670a2d185bc0be9ebd","tid":58533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161228/bkn-20161228111225024-1228_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161228%2Fbkn-20161228111225024-1228_00822_001.html&d=NcxA%2FjSO37%2BbTFwcb3mv0GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=6fb7b90a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161228/bkn-20161228111225024-1228_00822_001.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161228/photo/bkn-20161228111225024-1228_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161228135423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161228%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161228111225024-1228_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161228135423&h=95749e4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n被告何膺然今被判監21天，但因他已被還押21天，故此可獲即時釋放。(胡家豪攝) <br />\n<br />\n原定本月底退休的「老差骨」，今年初在九龍灣車輛扣留及檢驗中心當值期間，被揭藉管有扣押車輛車匙之便，在兩輛汽車內偷竊兩張八達通卡，繼而向港鐵注銷及取回餘額，他結果獲退款約150港元，卻為此陷牢獄之災，他早前承認兩項盜竊罪，今被判監21天，更有可能喪失長俸。 <br />\n<br />\n54歲被告何膺然今於觀塘法院被判監21天，但因他已被還押21天等候報告，故此他可獲即時釋放。被告自行求情指，被還押期間深明自由的寶貴，望法庭輕判。"},{"pid":"3e1ccbae91cf3e5f34a52f3e5f71a1f51db17518","tid":58533,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"下場如此，痛快。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675e0c51a02818b53b17e3dd2e90f3e95929ab60","tid":58533,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-